    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美国国债受创后亚洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于上周唐纳德·特朗普与乔·拜登进行辩论后，交易员们权衡了特朗普再次当选总统的可能性，亚洲股市预计将下跌，而该地区债券的价格可能跟随美国国债价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率上升导致亚洲美元贷款量跌至 14 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/asian-dollar-loan-volumes-plunge-to-14-year-low-as-rates-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元借贷成本上升，企业选择其他融资途径或尽可能推迟此类计划，今年上半年日本以外亚洲地区的美元贷款销售额跌至2010年以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/asian-dollar-loan-volumes-plunge-to-14-year-low-as-rates-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
